data.description: Welcome HOME to 335 Bridge Crossing Drive! This rare basement home is incredibly spacious and is centrally located to both downtown Simpsonville and Greenville. The curb appeal is amazing with all of the craftsman style and stone details. You'll also love the large front porch. As you enter the home, you'll be greeted with an exquisite two story foyer. Your eyes will then be drawn to the gorgeous LVP flooring that the owners have put in throughout the main level to bring in that desired consistency in flooring.  The sellers have also installed a convenient and beautiful drop zone between the garage entry and kitchen. This home is an entertainer's dream as it provides an open layout and many places to bring family and friends together.  The layout upstairs is amazing as you'll find four bedrooms, including the massive primary suite.  Two of the secondary bedrooms share a Jack and Jill bathroom. You'll also find a secondary bathroom and the walk in laundry room to complete this level. The fully finished walk out basement is complete with a recreation room, large bedroom, full bathroom and an huge and updated movie room that is wired for surround sound and HDMI connections. A wonderful unfinished storage room can also be found on this level. The basement walks out to a great patio area directly underneath the deck, which gives it the feel of a covered porch. The sellers have recently fenced in the back yard that now gives some extra privacy and security. Check out the 3D virtual tour for the floor-plan and schedule your showing now.
